          <p class="man-indent">
            Designs and evolves scalable system architectures, defines target<br />pictures and
            roadmaps, leads cross-functional teams including AI.<br />Bridges product, business, and
            engineering.
          </p>
          <p class="man-section">OPTIONS</p>
          <p class="man-indent">
            <span class="man-flag">--iSAQB-CPSA-A</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Certified Professional for
            Software Architecture
          </p>
          <p class="man-indent">
            <span class="man-flag">--iSAQB-CPSA-F</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Foundation Level
          </p>
          <p class="man-indent">
            <span class="man-flag">--location</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Germany,
